      <h1 class="post-title">Portugal: Como se Enterrou a Ferrovia para Coroar o Império do Pneu</h1>
      <p class="meta">Publicado em 2026-04-28 09:35:00</p>
      <figure class="post-thumb"><img src="https://fasgoncalves.github.io/fragmentoscaos-img/imagens/a3036962-24bb-4144-9dac-9b29fb7d8e55.jpg" alt=""></figure>
      <div class="post-content">
        <div style="background:#0b0b0b; color:#e8eef4; font-family:Georgia, serif; line-height:2.2; padding:10px; text-align:left;">

  <div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" style="display:none;">
    <meta itemprop="headline" content="Portugal: Como se Enterrou a Ferrovia para Coroar o Império do Pneu">
    <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2026-04-27T21:00:00+01:00">
    <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2026-04-27T21:00:00+01:00">
